title: chore: make codacy happy
message:
chore: make codacy happy

Various rules fixed:

useless parenthees & source format
replace deprecated code usage
avoid unused method parameters such as 'permissions'.
avoid unnecessary constructors - the compiler will generate these for you
switch statements should have a default label
fields should be declared at the top of the class, before any method declarations, constructors, initializers
'stations' could be replaced by a local variable
use equals() to compare object references
use explicit scoping instead of the default package private level
